## Shiny Flex Dashboard - Sales forecasting and anomaly detection

::: columns


::: {.column width="40%"}
![](images/Sales_Dashboard_shiny_flex.jpg)
:::


::: {.column width="5%"}
:::

::: {.column width="55%"}

This dashboard, built with Shiny Flex capability, looks at data from EverythingYouWillNeed.com website (___fake data___) to report out odaily product sales. You can select the product, the dates to analyze and click on apply to replicate the report, check sales forecast and anomalies for the specific product choice.

Giving your stakeholders the ability to play with product grain forecast and anomaly detection is a great was to get them on-board prior to deploying any model at scale. This Shiny dashboard was built specifically for that purpose.... [Link to play with the Shiny dashboard](https://hzon6a-deepsha-menghani.shinyapps.io/Sales_forecast_anomalies/){target=_blank}
:::


